---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 108
  - Title: Christ in Islam
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Phantom Flux of Life
---
The world is both seeking and sought. He who seeks the next world, this world
seeks him until his provision in it is complete; and he who seeks the present
world, the next world seeks him until death comes and seizes him by the neck.
